replies.body:
If wattpad's word count is correct, then I've got precisely 1500 words :D i don't know why i didn't start writing fanfictions about League of Legends sooner. There's so much to write about! The missing information in lores that make them intriguing. I really want to continue this story so I'll do exactly that on wattpad. Check it out (Isabelle999) I've spent 3 days analyzing every single champions' lore and champion page, so i really hope this story gets read (at least by two people) anyways, do vote honestly in the poll, i wouldn't mind if anyone said "why did you even try" i just want opinions plez! :D ok I'll stop naw. Byee!

